g disorders", "NEUROBIOLOGICAL FACTORS:Neurobiological factors, such as abnormalities in hormone levels and neurotransmitter function, are linked to eating disorders", "SOCIAL CULTURAL FACTORS:", "下丘脑-垂体-性腺轴:A neuroendocrine system regulating reproductive function, found to be hypoactive in some patients with anorexia nervosa"], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}